%e A219357 In A219324 (base 10), the smallest number greater than 10 is 247.
%t A219357 dcm[n_,b_] := (l = IntegerDigits[n,b]; Det[NestList[RotateRight, l, Length[l]-1]]); Table[i=b; While[dcm[i,b] != i, i++]; i, {b, 2, 43}]
